definitions.definition: ( derogatory , UK dialectal ) One who has done something offensive ; a deceitful , dishonest , or disreputable person; a deceiver ; a cheat .
( derogatory , UK dialectal , Scotland ) A rogue ; rascal ; miscreant ; a ne'er-do-well .

main_definition: ( derogatory , UK dialectal ) One who has done something offensive ; a deceitful , dishonest , or disreputable person; a deceiver ; a cheat .
secondary_definitions: ( derogatory , UK dialectal , Scotland ) A rogue ; rascal ; miscreant ; a ne'er-do-well .

definitions.definition: ( Canada , US , informal ) A truck driver .

main_definition: ( Canada , US , informal ) A truck driver .

definitions.definition: One who trucks or trafficks , by trade of goods; a trafficker .

main_definition: ( archaic or dialectal ) One who trucks or trafficks , by trade of goods; a trafficker .
